<p>Is there a way to combine polymer firebase-collection with iron-list?</p>  <p>I'm able to show my data with firebase-collection, but I also want to use iron-list to style my elements...</p>  <pre><code>&lt;firebase-collection data="{{games}}"                   location="url"&gt; &lt;/firebase-collection&gt;  &lt;template is="dom-repeat" items="{{games}}" as="game"&gt;     &lt;div&gt;       &lt;span&gt;{{game.home}}&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class="game_score"&gt;         &lt;span&gt;{{game.home_score}}&lt;/span&gt; - &lt;span&gt;{{game.away_score}}&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span&gt;{{game.away}}&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;/template&gt; </code></pre>